# Last-known-good running stack - baseline recorded 2026-07-07.
#
# These are the versions of the containers that were live and working before the
# version-tracking rework (chore/version-tracking-compose). The running images
# predate version stamping: their baked-in version is 0.0.0 (the old compose
# passed no APP_VERSION build arg), so these values are INFERRED from each
# image's build timestamp cross-referenced against the submodule's git tag
# history (newest tag whose creation time <= the image build time). Image IDs
# are exact (verified against the running containers), the versions are the best
# reconstruction.
#
# Caveats:
#   - medialab-jellyfin: image built 2026-06-26, but the earliest tag (v1.0.0)
#     is 2026-06-29. The running image is a PRE-v1.0.0 untagged main commit.
#   - medialab-orchestrator: image built 2026-06-29 14:14 EDT; v0.2.0 was tagged
#     14:51 EDT, 37 min later. So the running image is v0.1.0, not v0.2.0.
#
# To roll back to this state, rebuild each submodule at the version below (or
# pull the pinned image id if still present locally).

# torrent-downloader  image 25061b4ecf72  built 2026-06-26T22:35:11Z
TORRENT_DOWNLOADER_VERSION=1.2.0

# medialab-jellyfin    image 09963964ac2c  built 2026-06-26T22:34:53Z (pre-v1.0.0, untagged)
MEDIALAB_JELLYFIN_VERSION=0.0.0-pre-v1.0.0

# medialab-orchestrator image 634447667fb5 built 2026-06-29T18:14:53Z
MEDIALAB_ORCHESTRATOR_VERSION=0.1.0

# medialab-bot          image f22ba05e6040 built 2026-06-26T22:50:15Z
MEDIALAB_BOT_VERSION=1.0.0
